high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the kitchen island, then turn to your left and go to the garbage bin on the floor, past the counter, on your right.
Pull out the tomato that is in the garbage bin on the floor.
Turn to your right and go to the stove, then turn to your right again and go across the kitchen to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato on the on the bottom shelf of the refrigerator, to the right of the lettuce, in the freezer, wait a moment for the tomato to freeze, then remove the tomato from the freezer.
Turn around and go across the kitchen to the refrigerator, then turn left and go past the counter on your right, to the garbage bin on the floor to your right.
Put the tomato back in the garbage bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a frozen tomato in to garbage bin.

high_descs: Move forward, turn right to go towards the stove, turn left and move forward, then turn right to face the trash bin
Pick up a tomato from the trash bin.
Turn around and move forward, go left to the counter, then turn right and go forward to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside and chill it, then take it out.
Turn around and go to the stove ahead, turn left and go forward, then turn right to face the trash bin.
Put the tomato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the trash can.
Pick up the tomato in the trash can.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Cool the tomato in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the trash can.
Place the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To cool a tomato and place it in the trash can.
